credit.credit-words: O God of God, in whom combine

Be heaven, even now, our souls abode, Hid be our life with Christ in God, Our spirit, Lord, be one with thine; Let all our works in thee be wrought, And filled with thee be all our thought, Till in us thy full likeness shine.
